      "date": "2012-09-07 20:17:51.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nI built it here and it still failed\n\nhttps://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-master-fc15/167/arch=x86_64,build_type=client,distro=fc15,ib_stack=inkernel/console\n\nThis was built with kernel-2.6.38.6-26.rc1.fc15.x86_64.rpm and not \nkernel-2.6.38.6-26.fc15.x86_64.rpm same for kernel-devel.\n\nI don't know if this is important.\n\nI renamed to remove the rc1",
